 with at least 9 million cubic meters of molten matter. By early February, the sill had exceeded that threshold, and on February 8, another eruption began. A 3-kilometer-long fissure opened near the site of the December eruption, funneling lava away from Grindavík but toward a pipe that supplies hot water to much of the peninsula.\u003c/p>\n\u003cp>And so the cycle continues.\u003c/p>\n","fadein":false,"__typename":"ACFContent"},"$Post:135544.acf.modules.9":{"hide_this_component":null,"acf_fc_layout":"image_component","layout":"medium","regular_caption_right":true,"settings":"","attribution":"\u003cp>ZUMA Press Wire\u003c/p>\n","caption":"\u003cp>A fissure passes through one of Grindavík’s central streets.\u003c/p>\n","mobile_comp_caption":"","mobile_comp_attribution":"","sets":[{"type":"id","generated":true,"id":"$Post:135544.acf.modules.9.sets.0","typename":"ImageSet"}],"__typename":"ACFImageComponent"},"$Post:135544.acf.modules.9.sets.0":{"settings":"","image":{"type":"id","generated":true,"id":"$Post:135544.acf.modules.9.sets.0.image","typename":"Image"},"mobile_image":{"type":"id","generated":true,"id":"$Post:135544.acf.modules.9.sets.0.mobile_image","typename":"Image"},"mobile_side_margins":false,"mobile_width_constraint":"","mobile_caption":"","mobile_attribution":"","zoom_image":{"type":"id","generated":true,"id":"$Post:135544.acf.modules.9.sets.0.zoom_image","typename":"Image"},"zoom_caption":"","zoom_attribution":"","mobile_zoom_image":{"type":"id","generated":true,"id":"$Post:135544.acf.modules.9.sets.0.mobile_zoom_image","typename":"Image"},"mobile_zoom_caption":"","mobile_zoom_attribution":"","external_link":"","__typename":"ImageSet"},"$Post:135544.acf.modules.9.sets.0.image":{"alt":"A crack in Earth’s surface crosses a city street in a snowy scene with buildings and streetlights in the background.","caption":"","url":"https://d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net/uploads/2024/02/Grindavik-byRaul-Moreno_SOPA-Images-via-ZUMA-Press-Wire.webp","width":2201,"heigh